      • createMethodSummary

        public MethodSummaries createMethodSummary(String classpath,
                                           String methodSig)
        Creates a method summary for the method m It is assumed that only the default constructor of c is executed before m is called. The result of that assumption is that some fields of c may be null. A null field is not identified as a source and there for will not create a Field -> X flow.
        Parameters:
        classpath - The classpath containing the classes to summarize
        methodSig - method for which a summary will be created
        Returns:
        summary of method m
